RXE 1
ID driverctl
NAME Driver Control
ICON D
LAYOUT terminal
COLOR 0xFF4FC3B3
INPUT Command:
BUTTON Reload
USE APPKIT
UI PANEL 0 0 230 36 Installed drivers
UI BUTTON 8 8 82 20 Reload | reload
UI BADGE 118 9 86 18 DRFL
UI INPUT 0 46 220 24 Command:
UI OUTPUT 0 84 0 0 Driver output
DESKTOP 1
DOCK 1
TEXT Installed from the drivers branch. Use drivers reload after rxr install.
LANG C
CODE lsh("drivers reload");
CODE lsh("drivers");
